{"title":"尊严","authors":["黄堃"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":12,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"尊　严"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄　堃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军终于戒烟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当战死丛林的孙子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"馈赠的烟斗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回到他的桌前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用高射机枪弹壳制成的烟斗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即使在北方最寒冷的夜晚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也饱含温热"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"该抽烟的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老军人来到阳台，无言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看茫茫的天际，每一次"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他都看到孙子威武的背影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国当代军人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"体验最深的情感"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是理解"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而是沉默中的尊严"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}